                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The hill hears things. A plaque has been pressed already — good. The gardens talk to each other through the water, you know, and none of them called you a tourist."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Moss, orchard, terrace, pond. Finish the circle in any order, then climb back up to me."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Wei — the circle half walked",
                    Label: "in_progress__or3"
                },
                {
                    Priority: 10,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Where are the four gardens",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "OPEN_NAMED_DIALOG",
                                    Cmd: "stations"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "stations_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "I will walk them",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Up here we practice the old botany. Blossom holds the badge, but the badge grew out of four living gardens long before there was a building to keep it in."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "If you mean to challenge her, do it the old way. Walk the four gardens — moss court, orchard, terrace, pond. Best the warden of each, press your hand to the station plaque, and take its seal. Four seals, and this hill will bless your challenge."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Wei — the old botany",
                    Label: "default"
                },
                {
                    Priority: -1,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Back",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "OPEN_DEFAULT_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "back_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "To the gardens",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The moss court sits below this hill to the east, where the stones stay green all winter. Gardener Lin keeps it, and Lin does not hurry for anyone."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The orchard lies north in the low rows — Botanist Mei grafts there. The terrace hangs southeast over the water channels, that is Horticulturist Fang. And the pond is far south past the terrace, still as a held breath. Ranger Xiu watches it. Warden first, plaque second. The plaques know the difference."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Wei — naming the stations",
                    Label: "stations"
                },
                {
                    Priority: -1,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Thank you, Master Wei",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The stone came out of the moss court soil forty years ago and has been waiting on a worthy pocket ever since. Some of what you carry will know what to do with it."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Now go and see Blossom. Tell her the hill sent you — she will know what that costs me to say."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Wei — the handoff",
                    Label: "blessed"
                }
            ]
        },
